# Input

```scss
@include inline-comments(
1px,/* after positional block */
$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg:1px,// after keyword line
2px 4px 6px,/* before close */
);

@include inline-comments(
1px,// after positional line
$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg1:2px,/* after keyword block */
$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg2:10,
2px 4px 6px// before close line
);

@include separator-line-comments(
1px // separator line
, 2px
);

@include nested-parameter-separator-line-comments(
fn(
1px // nested separator line
, 2px
)
);

```


# Formatted

```scss
@include inline-comments(
	1px,
	/* after positional block */
	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg:
		1px,
	// after keyword line
	2px 4px 6px /* before close */
);

@include inline-comments(
	1px,
	// after positional line
	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg1:
		2px,
	/* after keyword block */
	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg2:
		10,
	2px 4px 6px // before close line
);

@include separator-line-comments(
	1px, // separator line
	2px
);

@include nested-parameter-separator-line-comments(
	fn(
		1px, // nested separator line
		2px
	)
);

```

# Lines exceeding max width of 80 characters
```
    4: 	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg:
   13: 	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg1:
   16: 	$very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-very-long-arg2:
```
